headline: 2 Concrete & Aggregates Stocks Riding the Infrastructure Boom
summary: Federal infrastructure spending should help the Zacks Building Products - Concrete & Aggregates industry players like VMC and MLM. Yet, high rates and expenses are risks.

headline: 2 High-Flying Stocks for Long-Term Investors and 1 We Brush Off
summary: Expensive stocks typically earn their valuations through superior growth rates that other companies simply can’t match. The flip side though is that these lofty expectations make them particularly susceptible to drawdowns when market sentiment shifts.
